The paper discusses the structure of scientific research and uses network analysis to map the landscape of interconnected research topics. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Sound and Music Computing (cs.SD), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Computers and Society (cs.CY). However, given the focus on network analysis and interdisciplinary research, cs.SI and cs.SD are the most likely categories, followed by cs.DL, cs.IR, and cs.CY.
